Dan Bernstein - did the original checkpassword
Jedi/Sector One - did a plain text version of checkpassword. I borrowed few
line of code from him.
RSA Labs. - did the md5c.c and hold copyrights over it (read the source)
RFC 2104 authors - provided sample implementation of HMAC which i have used.
Erwin Hoffmann - changed order of auth parameters to more conformity
GNU Foundation - crypt functionality and code

Gentoo Foundation - for their great distribution, especially portage, eudev 
and openrc (includes to not adapt systemd overall without any thoughs)
